{"product_id": "12100", "page": 12, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-12-31", "text": "If you have Windows 10, Get a Patch and you're good to go.\nSome aspects of the shooting haven't aged well. Plus, the driving feels like you're on ice.\nBut there's something magical about playing GTA III again.\nIt's aged like swiss cheese honestly, but it's still pretty tasty.\nJust exploring this incarnation of Liberty City again is beautiful honestly.\nAlso hearing stuff like \"Yup I've been drinking again\" or \"In the navy!\" Takes you back to a much more simplier time.\nWhen video games were getting more advanced but we were blurring that fine line between advancement and nostalgia.\nOverall, purchase GTA III to see a relic of how modern video games have shaped up to be in nearly 17 years.", "hours": 7.5, "user_id": "76561198068978307", "username": "KatamarisWrath", "products": 354, "early_access": false}
