{"product_id": "12100", "page": 31, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-07-25", "text": "Classic Game!!! Stands the test of time.\nIn order to get it to play on windows 10 I did the following:\n1. RC shortcut, goto properties, added -norestrictions one space behind Title.\n2. Set compatibility to WinXP PS3.\n3. Upon start up I couldn't see menu, I arrowed down to options and right arrowed, as I did the screen became clearer with each increase. Started game and now I can adjust the resolution both in and out of game, also upon restart the main menus appeared. Now playing @ 3840x2160 .\nIn my opinion the best game in the series, groundbreaking 3D rendering at the time. I played the originals and this is what I thought of when I did lol.", "hours": 1.9, "username": "LEAFmeALONE", "products": 254, "early_access": false}
