{"product_id": "12100", "page": 58, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-01", "text": "Windows 10 (and judging from forum posts, 7 and 8.1 also) users:\nBe aware that this game is old and will probably not run on your PC. Mine worked fine for a day, now it crashes immediately when I try to start it. Same for VC, by the way. To give you an overview of what I tried:\n- compatibility modes\n- running as admin\n- deleting gta.set\n- adding the game to DEP\n- Silentpatch\n- download ddraw.dll\n- deleting savegames\n- copying savegames to different User Files directory\n- reinstalling\nSooo... Be careful what you buy. I usually buy old games from a different platform that actually patches them to run on modern systems *shrug* sort of expected this here too.\n---\nIf you got an old PC I 100% recommend this game. Played it as a kid and loved it, still do today. Kind of disappointed I can't continue playing :(", "hours": 2.4, "username": "Zuhani", "products": 30, "early_access": false}
