{"product_id": "12100", "page": 64, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-06", "text": "Does this game even need another review? Nevertheless here it is. Of course this game is absolutely amazing. I was playing GTA 1&2 when i probably shouldn't have been. hen i saw the first trailer for GTA 3 back in 2001, i couldn't believe it. Even at that young age i knew this would change everything. None of my friends understood why i was so excited aside from what it was, because i had played the first 2 and knew what we were in for. No one understood why it was titled GTA 3 because they had never heard of GTA 1 or 2 and were thinking it was a new title. he Grand Theft Auto series has come a long way, but nothing will ever compare to the \"original\". after 15 years this is still my favorite one and i still get full enjoyment everytime i play it.", "hours": 15.5, "user_id": "76561198031618050", "username": "wb94509", "products": 114, "early_access": false}
