{"product_id": "12100", "page": 74, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-21", "text": "Grand Theft Auto 3 is the great transitioning of the old Grand Theft Auto formula into a fully realized open world gameplay. Grand Theft Auto 3 was developed and published by Rockstar and Take-Two Interactive.\nGrand Theft Auto 3 is revolutionary for bringing about the realization of a 3D open world game in the bustling mimicry of New York known as Liberty City. The possibilities in Grand Theft Auto 3 are truly up to you. Jack cars, drive off cliffs, start a massacre, jump off buildings and bridges, hook up with P rostitutes, work for crime syndicates...the least of what is possible in this game and it's sequels is entirely up to the persons choice, a relic of freedom in gaming.", "hours": 92.0, "username": "Sirius Waker", "products": 272, "early_access": false}
