{"product_id": "12100", "page": 91, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-31", "text": "First 3D GTA.\nEven though it doesnt have many features (compared to GTA:SA) its my favorite one in the series. Also has not very popular multiplayer mod which is awesome for such old game BUT all servers are dead because of hackers. For that I wont rate it as either positive or negative one.\n+Story\n+Side Missions\n+Gangs\n+Cheats and Mods\n+Old grandma with shopping bags high-kicking you in the face\n+Drugs\n+Bad\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665mute MC\n-No customizing (except pay'n'spray and 8bomb)\n-No (motor)bikes\n-No helicopters\n-Doesnt support gamepads natively", "hours": 7.7, "username": "stupefaction", "products": 263, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12100", "page": 91, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-26", "text": "It's a good game. I really had a hard time doing some of the missions.\nThe traffic and PED is tricky but working better as Vice City.\nI managed to complete the game in 16 hours and had a great time. The game had me both laughing and mad at times.\nIt's a good, old school GTA game.\nIt's just difficult that the pay'n spray icons are not displayed on the map.\nNor are the ammu-nation locations or any locations of interest. Except for the missions.\nThere is no map button, no way to see the map. Sometimes the game asks you to go to a certain location and you have no idea where that place might be.\nThere is an annoying bridge sound you hear from afar when the bridge opens, pretty annoying.\nPretty good game if you ask me. Worth the 10 bucks.", "hours": 16.2, "username": "Tomboeg", "products": 650, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12100", "page": 92, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-01-25", "text": "This game has everything. Solid storyline with multiple betrayals, various missions, unforgettable radio stations, powerful weapons, gang wars, fast cars, dumb police and almost immortal main character.\nIf you wanna feel a few years younger for a moment.....If you wanna be the king of crime.....If you wanna kill people and destroy everything movable......you shold not hesitate anymore.", "hours": 19.5, "user_id": "76561198136507609", "username": "jz", "products": 24, "early_access": false}
