{"product_id": "12100", "page": 129, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-03-28", "text": "My fave GTA game. I love GTA games but GTA III will always be the best in my eyes. This is what set the standards in sandbox gaming.\nGreat story\nGreat cars and handling physics\nAwesome Soundtrack/Radio stations - Chatterbox FM, Head Radio & Rise FM\nLoads of gangs\nWell crafted and easy to navigate islands\nNice graphics\nHumorus Pedestrains\nAwesome jumps/stunts\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nHard to aim, fire weapons (recommend X360 pad with mod)\nToo much mission reward money ($3000 to pick up Misty!?)\nCant swim (drown if water reaches waist)\nHard to get through islands without being shot at (especially in Portland)\nUnbalanced health loss", "hours": 13.7, "user_id": "76561198006247927", "username": "Trigonometry", "products": 76, "early_access": false}
