{"product_id": "12100", "page": 133, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-28", "text": "Great game, although one that didn't age as well as the others.\nVery basic compared to nowadays.\n-No jumping out of moving vehicles\n-No limb based damaged, headshot is as good as a body shot if it isn't a sniper.\n-Jumping and touching anything will cause you to flinch\n-No in game map\n-No blips for pay n spray or Ammunation after a certain point\n-Expresso 2 go is complete \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665.\nDefinately a classic, these are only things that came with being the first to pioneer this genre, which doesn't make it bad at all.", "hours": 9.1, "username": "Mc Chan", "products": 398, "early_access": false}
