{"product_id": "12100", "page": 135, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-01-09", "text": "The very first time GTA went 3rd person and it was AWESOME.\nThe game is a legend. For the first time you can do everything a GTA had to offer while living it inside the game and not above it.\nThe main character was not voiced yet at that time, but the game is still awesome, with a crazy story twist of events and weird-funny characters.\nAlthough roaming sandbox games existed before this title, this one certaily was the very best 3rd person full 3D graphics sandbox game at the time.\nI was glad to had the chance to play this from start to end and if you ever get the chance to start a GTA marathon, you won't be any disappointed!\nTotally recommended! For old times' sake!", "hours": 19.0, "username": "Zweis\u2020ein ( \u0ca0_\u0ca0)", "products": 261, "found_funny": 7, "early_access": false}
