{"product_id": "12100", "page": 147, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-08-28", "text": "Grand Theft Auto III... been almost 14 years I believe since released, and still is a huge success as it was the first GTA game to be featured in 3-D. Before I had Steam, I played this on my PlayStation 2 and then bought the CD-ROM version of it.. was not any difference really but I still prefer it over GTA Vice City, San Andreas, Liberty City Stories, and GTA IV (not GTA V though, because it is way better!) since this game of all GTA games, is by far the goriest if you have not noticed... And that Claude Speed as a mute, makes him by far the best GTA protagonist of the entire Grand Theft Auto Franchise.. Since nothing is better than a mute human (lol). If you like GTA games, do not waste your time and buy this one now! you'll love it! I know I do...", "hours": 2.4, "username": "Diabl\u00f3n.", "products": 144, "early_access": false}
