{"product_id": "12100", "page": 173, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-11-26", "text": "It's an old game, and you can see that on both graphic and gameplay sides.\nBut yeah, this is the first 3D GTA game! And my first 3D GTA too.\nIt's kind of GTA2, but in 3D, it's enjoyable for what it is but it's not aged so well and this can lead to some frustration. However is still totally playable and it's surely a classic. Worth checking if you want to learn a bit of open-world history, but I still prefer GTA2.", "hours": 31.9, "username": "Dunther", "products": 3748, "early_access": false}
