{"product_id": "12100", "page": 184, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-07-26", "text": "This game came out in 2001. By those standards, this game was golden. A full 3D city to drive around, shoot, and get into trouble. Set the standard for modern sandbox games. By today's standard it doesn't fare so well. Besides the main missions there isn't much to do, and it has very limited graphics for today. It also has issues with modern systems. Widescreen does not work so you'll need to turn that off to achieve 16:9 resolutions properly. I recommend it because this is a gem of video game history. I personally enjoy playing old games, but it requires a lot of patience. 9/10", "hours": 13.5, "username": "Raz", "products": 302, "early_access": false}
